single ?:
  symbol ?
double ??:
  symbol ??
tilde alone:
  symbol ~
tilde-prefixed identifier:
  symbol ~D
  symbol ~Var
name-prefixed by tilde, suffixed by something:
  symbol n~
  symbol i~
double tilde (iteration counter):
  symbol ~~
tilde plus dot plus identifier:
  symbol ~D
  . .
  symbol X
tilde plus question:
  symbol ~?
tilde plus ?+ (auto-closure increment):
  symbol ~i
  + +
tilde collect form:
  symbol ~x
  . .
  symbol Q
  symbol ~x
  [] (#Q)
tilde with default:
  symbol ~var
  ^ ^
  symbol Default
single ? alone vs with operator:
  symbol ?
  + +
  symbol ?
  * *
  symbol ?
